TOPIC: ROLES IN ANSIBLE
===========================

vim main.yml

---
- hosts: dev
  connection: ssh

  roles:
    - pranay
    - babu
    - devops
    - aws

:wq

in above what the names roles we given in playbook should be a folders with that names

first we need to create one folder for roles-------> in that roles folder we need to create sub folders with roles name like 4 roles mkdir pranay babu devops aws---
-------> first go to 1st folder pranay role folder----> cd pranay/-------> in this pranay folder need to create task folder with name task-----> mkdir task----->
-------> in this task folder we need to create yaml file as main.yml file---------> cd tasks/----> vim main.yml-------> in here we need to write ansible playbook
--------> 

